  // Set the reporter to use the Mocha reporter
  config.reporter = 'mocha';

  // Set the reporter options
  config.reporterOptions = {
    printFiles: true,
    printSummary: true,
    printDetails: true,
  };

  return config;
};```

**`cypress/support/index.js` file:**
```module.exports = (on, config) => {
  // Add a command to take a screenshot on failure
  on('fail', (error) => {
    // Get the current test context
    const { context } = error;

    // Take a screenshot of the failed test
    context.screenshot('failure');
  });
};```

**`cypress/integration/example.spec.js` file:**
```describe('Example Test', () => {
